### ============================================================
### Feature 1 — Analytics Dashboard — HTTP Test Requests
### ============================================================
### Usage: Open in VS Code REST Client extension or IntelliJ HTTP Client.
### Replace {{token}} with a valid JWT for ROLE_ADMIN or ROLE_RECEPTIONIST.
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ─── AUTH (get a token first) ───────────────────────────────

### Login as Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@hotel.com",
  "password": "yourPassword"
}

###

### ─── DASHBOARD ENDPOINTS ────────────────────────────────────

### 1. GET /api/dashboard/summary
### Returns: totalRooms, occupiedRooms, availableRooms, occupancyRate,
###          todayCheckIns, todayCheckOuts, activeBookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2. GET /api/dashboard/revenue?range=7d
### Returns: array of { date, revenue } for the last 7 days (PAID only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/revenue?range=7d
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. GET /api/dashboard/revenue?range=30d
### Returns: array of { date, revenue } for the last 30 days
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/revenue?range=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. GET /api/dashboard/booking-status-breakdown
### Returns: array of { status, count } grouped by BookedStatus
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/booking-status-breakdown
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. GET /api/dashboard/recent-activity
### Returns: top 5 most recent events (bookings + payments merged by timestamp)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/recent-activity
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── NEGATIVE TESTS ────────────────────────────────────────

### 6. Access summary as GUEST → should return 403 Forbidden
### (use a guest JWT here)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer GUEST_JWT_HERE

###

### 7. Access summary with no token → should return 401 Unauthorized
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary

###
